### Get all Todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todo
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Todo by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/todo/3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create a new Todo
POST http://localhost:3000/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Todo",
  "completed": false
}

###

### Update a Todo
PUT http://localhost:3000/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Updated Todo",
  "completed": true
}

###

### Delete a Todo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json

